    * Minor patch to solve memomy issue (#94) on Mac OS X

Version 1.4.2
=============

    * Use the news virtual_memory() and virtual_swap() fct (PsUtil)
    * Display "Top process" in logs
    * Minor patch on man page for Debian packaging
